Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,久能先生  是個沒見過的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別管他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:02.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是個小鬼是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是弄錯地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:11.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:17.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫紅真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:20.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我找少當家久能正先生有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:25.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,花村幼稚園的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼設計啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:14.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,少當家久能正先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫紅真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我們原來見過面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:21.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  去查一下紅真九郎這人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:33.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那種小鬼 把他幹掉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道花村幼稚園的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:39.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我來是因為有人騷擾花村幼稚園的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:39.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,騷擾？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:40.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:45.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,上週園長的家被人潛入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,土地的權利證書被偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:51.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,留下了園長孫子的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是無言的恐嚇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟警察商量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就會傷害到孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這與我們事務所有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係？這是你指使的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,花村幼稚園什麼的聽都沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:16.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你準備把花村幼稚園以及旁邊的土地買下然後轉讓是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:21.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有久能先生指使購買花村幼稚園土地的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:25.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還有部下回覆的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:31.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這些是每天打到園長家裡的無聲電話的號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這能作為民事案件解決嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:39.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅君  你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,糾紛調解人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,糾紛調解人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:47.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那你希望什麼交易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,請把土地的權利證書還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:55.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還有請保證今後不對花村幼稚園出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我能得到什麼好處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我們銷毀掌握的所有情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:01.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些就想讓我收手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:07.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你要怎麼讓我相信你銷毀了掌握的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那只能靠你相信我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真敢說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:13.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,又沒其它辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,久能先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:15.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:18.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙認識的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是一個人來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哎  誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:24.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什麼可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來找真九郎的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:27.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:32.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  你說過要保護紫的卻跑到這種地方來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還帶著小孩來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:35.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你在我睡著的時候總是做這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了不能到外面來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:44.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小子  沒法談了  今天你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  那交易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我把證據散播出去你也不在乎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那樣麻煩的是久能先生你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:57.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:58.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:04.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,久能先生  我掌握的情報一定會全部銷毀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:09.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:20.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你之後絕對不再對花村幼稚園出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  送客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  紫  回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  這傢伙很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫  別說這麼失禮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:39.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  糾紛調解人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:46.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都寫在你臉上了  騙子就是一副騙子的嘴臉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:46.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  久能先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  別相信這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:51.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:56.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,糾紛調解人  趕緊走  到我忍耐的極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:07:00.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是  這就走  這傢伙人有點怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.58,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別把我當傻瓜  有哪點奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不要點頭哈腰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:07.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:08.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:12.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不要生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:15.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎竟然相信那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  紫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:32.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:37.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,住手  放開他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:39.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:42.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:43.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:48.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:51.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不要  放手  放…手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,骨頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:57.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是  崩月的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:01.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是件重大的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:25.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是要與九鳳院家為敵的相當重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:25.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,彌生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不知道這孩子有多麼重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,給他好好說明就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:33.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然把她留在公寓然後自己跑到黑幫事務所去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:36.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太不小心了  你把這工作當什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:38.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,粗心大意  想法也太天真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都輕易下結論才會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,彌生  冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:49.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,說到底  這不是你這種程度的男人能接手的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:58.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事也是會有的  今後你會注意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:09:59.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:02.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們今天就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:04.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:09.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅香大人  我實在是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有交給你來做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為交給男人來做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:15.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:22.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,除我之外  明明還能找到很多能夠保護她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏選紅真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:27.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都說過是我的直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:29.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是懷疑紅香大人的直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:34.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  通過今天的事  紅香大人應該也很明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這工作對紅真九郎來說太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:42.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,他實力不足這點我很清楚  十分清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:43.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,現在先饒了我吧  以後會給你好好說明的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我要繼續留在這
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:54.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,早安  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:23.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體不疼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:27.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了  早飯由紫來做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:30.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫  昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:36.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:39.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有好好聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,讓真九郎挨揍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:44.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,錯的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是紫的任意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你生我的氣也是理所當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:54.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,錯的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:57.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉上有寫著騙人兩字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:03.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你平安無事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的早飯就交給紫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎好好休息就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這個還能吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:18.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  睡眠不足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:21.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天看了晚間直播吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:22.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那個真好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:26.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,後藤這女生感覺不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  後藤她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是防守方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:37.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小紫  你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:38.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,看不出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這房間什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,臭的不是被子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:53.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  一般進房間的時候總該敲個門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:55.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這可是新聞社的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,新聞社的社員只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:00.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  這是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,把其他社員趕出去的是誰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你是來報告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,順利解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可以對園長說沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大概可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大概  真不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我總之是去解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:19.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不知他們是否就此收手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:20.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:26.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只是摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,和他們起爭執了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:38.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這圓珠筆真便利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:39.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,上次也被外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是俄羅斯人吧  問路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:43.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你大意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是涉及小紫的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:56.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:57.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是其他工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:00.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:04.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,作為崩月家的人  忠告一句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:09.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要用到角的工作別接比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:10.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我拿傷藥來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:16.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有爺爺做的為不成熟的弟子所準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:17.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:24.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:26.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:30.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼把被子擺在我房間門口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在曬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡採光點最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎的被子臭得受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去對身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,確實  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才在幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:49.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不成熟  不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:50.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你確實不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我的被子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為了少女的健康我才允許放在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:11.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  變得乾淨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今天環教我打掃房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎的被子也曬在走廊裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:26.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我住在這裡  偶爾也該打掃一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:27.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還有骯髒的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要洗頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:53.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快看  真九郎  我終於成功獨自洗頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,塗洗髮精很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:01.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,滲進去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:02.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:07.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  還疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因我的錯  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是紫的錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:22.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我有許多舊傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕是處理糾紛事件的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,像勳章一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可以先出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:35.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:39.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和真九郎待同樣時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,數到20就出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4  5  6  7  8
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:44.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今天能看到星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,明早會很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:53.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,呐  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:54.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:59.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎為什麼要當糾紛調解人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:04.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為憧憬紅香小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:09.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:10.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅香是那麼好的女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:19.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,比起紫  環  暗繪  夕乃還要好的女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:24.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是作為女人的角度  只是想變得像紅香小姐那樣強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:28.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我在和紫一樣大的時候還很膽小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:29.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:31.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎小時候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:35.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,很無聊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道許多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫也想變強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:39.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,強？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:40.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,想變強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:43.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,綁架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:51.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  把機場炸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:54.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,擄走存活下來的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅在那之中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,雙親在那時候去世的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:03.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,已經超過危險  害怕之類的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:04.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:06.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,非常疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸沒有感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:11.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,會有這種事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,腦中一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:18.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,死都不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:19.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:22.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:30.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  有什麼好笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你  想死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,行啊  死也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真囂張  既然想死就成全你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,住手  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,明明想死的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候那個人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:07.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們這類專家才能完成的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就一會的工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:29.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊  將孩子帶到外面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:31.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:32.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:34.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:37.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了  來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟隨了紅香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不久就寄宿在夕乃家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,學了八年崩月流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:50.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然非常辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因此也擁有了如今的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:56.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:00.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅香  讓我成為了糾紛調解人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:03.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為真九郎的努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,現在才剛剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很像  那兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:15.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只有真九郎才能理解紫的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:20.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此他的力量還…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我有個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:25.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那是很久之前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:34.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一天能把小姐  紫帶到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:35.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:38.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不知道怎麼做才拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就算去外面了又怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:44.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡什麼也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:48.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡就會有與我同樣的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:49.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮丈大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:55.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經生下了三個小孩  已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,期待蓮丈大人也沒用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:02.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓紫擁有與我同樣的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮丈大人也不會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:08.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮丈大人可是愛著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:11.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人無法捨棄九鳳院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:13.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:15.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我很感謝他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:22.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,比起迄今為止裡之院的女人來說我是很自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:25.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  想讓紫去見識外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:28.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要擁有比我更美好的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是困難的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,能請你接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  她已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:43.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是紫的親生母親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:45.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,九鳳院蒼樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒能戰勝家族規矩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:53.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在九鳳院工作過我才知道  那家族很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:57.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,看著年幼的紫  我覺得必須接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:01.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這對真九郎來說太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:06.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  對他來說也是有好處的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:09.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,想保護誰的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:11.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,會讓人變強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:14.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我如此堅信著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:17.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我去大久保了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:18.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:20.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我走著去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:21.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是去五月雨莊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:22.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,情況我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:28.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還是擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:30.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.30,0:24:21.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,下集  紅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:24.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,願望
